<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/how-the-media-misrepresents-the-debate-over-the-green-new-deal/">How the Media Misrepresents the Debate Over the Green New Deal</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Thereâ€™s more to the story than â€œenvironmentalists versus blue-collar workers.â€</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/michelle-chen/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Michelle Chen</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://inthesetimes.com/working/entry/21930/green-new-deal-politico-blue-collar-workers-climate-media-ocasio-cortez' itemprop='url'>In These Times</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2019-06-21T15:26:45+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2019-06-21T15:26:45+00:00">June 21, 2019</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
